      "title": "PROVER VERIFIER\nHold a valid coloring ϕ : V → {1, . . . , k}\nSample a fresh permutation π ∈ Sk and fresh\nrv for all v ∈ V\nCompute cv = f\n\nπ(ϕ(v)), rv\n\nfor all v ∈ V\nSet C = {cv}v∈V\nC\n−−−−−→\nSample a uniform random edge (u, v) ∈ E\n(u,v) ←−−−−−−−\nReveal (π(ϕ(u)), ru) and (π(ϕ(v)), rv)\n(π(ϕ(u)),ru), (π(ϕ(v)),rv)\n−−−−−−−−−−−−−−−−−−−−→\nAccept if\n(u, v) ∈ E\nf(π(ϕ(u)), ru) = cu and\nf(π(ϕ(v)), rv) = cv\nπ(ϕ(u)), π(ϕ(v)) ∈ {1, . . . , k} and\nπ(ϕ(u)) ̸= π(ϕ(v))",
